{"tid":2453149,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"志雲嘲港台極偏極倚 李百全係「生抽王」 秋生旁白節目都遭殃「佢鍾意點就點」","createTime":"2021-03-19T09:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:26:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8d2554594b0de6f209a00d64e00d95714f9a57","tid":2453149,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210319/JYZAFEZIVNB5TI53NF6REC4MQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210319%2FJYZAFEZIVNB5TI53NF6REC4MQY%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=d9183ff4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210319%2FJYZAFEZIVNB5TI53NF6REC4MQY%2F&h=17207e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210319/JYZAFEZIVNB5TI53NF6REC4MQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n志雲嘲港台極偏極倚 李百全係「生抽王」<br />\n秋生旁白節目都遭殃「佢鍾意點就點」<br />\n<br />\n廣播處長李百全自本月1日履新後，親自審查港台節目，相繼把他認為「不合格」的節目或內容抽走，最新受影響的節目包括黃秋生、譚小環以及被捕的港台前編導蔡玉玲有份參與的節目及劇集。對於被稱為「獨裁皇帝」李百全的行為，黃秋生昨日謂：「佢鍾意點就點啦，反正我幫佢多過佢幫我！」譚小環稱平常心看待，陳志雲則在商台節目批評港台現時極偏極倚，更嘲李百全為「生抽王」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【續牌風波】商台新城同受壓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/leqwHbw8BA2LqYLM4IVLFZd3Tfo=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J6LTQWLADZHOXAEZ33H35PIJRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FleqwHbw8BA2LqYLM4IVLFZd3Tfo%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ6LTQWLADZHOXAEZ33H35PIJRY.jpg&h=84963255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■秋生前年也曾為港台節目《聽出好戲勢》作旁白，他當時表示能讓視障人士也可體會睇電視的樂趣。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n李百全上任廣播處長至今只有19日，已化身為港台節目「劊子手」，繼之前連環臨時抽起《香港故事》中組合LMF及作家蔣曉薇的訪問，以及前立法會議員李華明任嘉賓的《議事論事》後，前日傳李百全再手起刀落，抽起港台前編導蔡玉玲有份參與的《卓越教室》、譚小環主演的短劇《環顧日常》及黃秋生為視障人士旁白的節目《聽出好戲勢》，李百全連番對節目「政治審查」，引起外界非議。<br />\n<br />\n....................................得個人被針對？他則指：「我都費事諗，佢鍾意點就點啦，反正我幫佢多過佢幫我，又唔係搵錢，諗住幫吓港台做啲有意義嘅嘢啫。」其實秋生在前年也曾為《聽出好戲勢》作旁白，當時還特地為節目拍攝宣傳片，節目目前仍能在港台YouTube收看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Tp8R73GNnTKeNWAtp1-krpWheSI=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ACK6OJXSAZBCJIC72VSAP4FBFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTp8R73GNnTKeNWAtp1-krpWheSI%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FACK6OJXSAZBCJIC72VSAP4FBFQ.jpg&h=5976e710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■秋生日前在fb上載自拍自導的新片，他笑說是「跟後生學嘢」。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XS5T58EWJ424SHTMA_QhpA21Atg=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5CJBCNUCZVESBPACG4TNTNMUTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXS5T58EWJ424SHTMA_QhpA21Atg%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5CJBCNUCZVESBPACG4TNTNMUTA.jpg&h=dd7e9a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李百全上任廣播處長僅僅19日，已有多個節目被抽起，被網民嘲是「劊子手」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚小環平常心應對<br />\n<br />\n譚小環昨早即在Ig貼出拍《環顧日常》的花絮照片，並留言：「我作為演員，一直用心去演，希望大家會睇到我的演出，我信總有機會在不同的平台上會睇到。」還hashtag了「平常心」，小環老公「渣哥」蔡強榮也在fb留言力撐：「感謝新任處長認證。」他又tag「譚小環正式宣佈加入全港失業大軍」。《蘋果》昨日聯絡小環，但至截稿前未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲昨日在商台雷霆881節目《在晴朗的一天出發》中，直指李百全抽起節目是要交代：「𠵱家好似要變成極偏極倚，真係要解釋，點講《卓越教室》講教育都要抽起？係唔係蔡玉玲呢三個字已經變成敏感字，唔出得呢？」他又批評商務及經濟發展局..............................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nZa9vCHfMSeWtIq5cpOSxwsTtVI=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L73KYZIM4FHJZNTTWGDYR5BVUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnZa9vCHfMSeWtIq5cpOSxwsTtVI%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL73KYZIM4FHJZNTTWGDYR5BVUU.jpg&h=323351dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚小環（左二）演出的另一部港台短劇《格外樓神》上月如常播出，至今仍可在港台網站收看。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WIYub5KCAdNuBwB9VEg0N3KSZtU=/802x367/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RBGASMTZYREEHMDVT365IB2CPM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWIYub5KCAdNuBwB9VEg0N3KSZtU%3D%2F802x367%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRBGASMTZYREEHMDVT365IB2CPM.gif&h=e413f2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚小環主演的《環顧日常》被抽起，她昨日在社交網貼出花絮照，老公渣哥也有留言力撐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Oqptdnsqew-gxLuqrggnVMgyRU4=/802x1797/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TYDGOBNWHZGPFOUS5FRFHQ5BOI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOqptdnsqew-gxLuqrggnVMgyRU4%3D%2F802x1797%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTYDGOBNWHZGPFOUS5FRFHQ5BOI.gif&h=db805b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港台前編導蔡玉玲負責、潘杰寧主持（下圖）的《卓越教室》是與教育局合作的節目，內容並不涉及政治，卻同樣被禁播。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧覓雪：係針對個人<br />\n<br />\n盧覓雪則在商台叱咤903節目《在晴朗的一天出發》批評：「根據𠵱家嘅內容睇，係針對個人唔係針對件事，乜都可以抽起。咁搵叻哥（陳百祥）做《城市論壇》、何議員拍《鏗鏘集》，有大把愛國藝人全部排住隊去拍任何港台節目。」另一主持林海峰也笑說：「佢睇節目都有排睇，邊有時間同啲工會見面。抽起好恐怖。再係咁抽起，可能只有重播（節目）。」盧覓雪續道重播《暢談普通話》最安全最好，林海峰笑言：「24小時播《暢談普通話》，再加啲海浪同自然聲咁。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，去年底到台灣工作的秋生，在本月初已回港，近日他完成隔離後，在fb分享一條自編、自導、自演...........................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BAOgrAsHJdMGZTIlYaFKIfe6TZc=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CQEJ5JXMLFCRZN6K7BDEZR54WI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBAOgrAsHJdMGZTIlYaFKIfe6TZc%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCQEJ5JXMLFCRZN6K7BDEZR54WI.jpg&h=2c6849a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳志雲在商台節目直指「蔡玉玲」這三個字現在已經變成敏感字。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HWrSXjapwOU_ktCtfPU1twyh2ZE=/802x540/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G24GDTFQHVD4DBSVZVEZ74RRYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHWrSXjapwOU_ktCtfPU1twyh2ZE%3D%2F802x540%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG24GDTFQHVD4DBSVZVEZ74RRYA.jpg&h=baa59432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■盧覓雪（右）昨日直指現在是針對人而非事件，林海峰（中）則笑說港台之後可能只能重播節目。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ViDqsFzaIRT48EEL0kv_Ea72LF4=/802x297/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZQT7Q4NZSRCVDEY4WUXKR73MQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FViDqsFzaIRT48EEL0kv_Ea72LF4%3D%2F802x297%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZQT7Q4NZSRCVDEY4WUXKR73MQA.gif&h=f6a5c542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■因參與初選被補的嚴重弱智人士家長協會前主席李芝融（左圖），與因蠔涌爆炸品案被判入獄三年十個月的彭艾烈，在《香港故事》的訪問同樣被抽起。資料圖片"}]}